## ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’» Development

Requirements: Python 3.10+

```bash
# Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/whoisjayd/yt-study.git
cd yt-study

# Install dependencies (using uv is recommended)
pip install uv
uv sync

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Run locally
uv run yt-study --help
```